io.confluent.ksql.analyzer

Class RewrittenAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.analyzer.RewrittenAnalysis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImmutableAnalysis

    public class RewrittenAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
implements ImmutableAnalysis
    A wrapper for an ImmutableAnalysis that rewrites all expressions using a given rewriter plugin (as provided to ExpressionTreeRewriter). This is useful when planning queries to allow the planner to transform expressions as needed it builds up the transformations needed to execute the query.
